Functions to remember
np.ones
np.zeros

np.argmax(arr) -> index containing max values
np.argmin(arr) -> index containing min val
np.argsort(arr) -> array of indices as per sorting

use dtype to specify data type of elements in matrix

np.arange(6).reshape(3,2) 
-> an array of 6 elements from 0-5 -> 2d array of 3X2 
reshape can be used to form 3d array as well

and reshape function on arange

Follow Structured array tutorial it is good , new insights 

